{"tid":966534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本季會到中國出差 蘋果CEO庫克：不擔心被抓","createTime":"2019-01-03T01:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T03:12:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf432547357b8d4b0c0b8c268b5d3b3161d5f58","tid":966534,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/01/03/realtime/5743753.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2Frealtime%2F5743753.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=84fae5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國財經網站CNBC報導，即使中國電信巨擘華為公司財務長孟晚舟因美國壓力12月在加大拿大被捕， 蘋果公司執行長庫克表示，他並不擔心到中國出差，不理外界對中國可能採取報復行動的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n庫克受訪時說：「我10月在那裡。本季稍晚還會過去。所以我甚至不去想那些事。」<br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟上月被捕凸顯中美之間持續未歇的貿易緊張，引發外界揣測中國可能瞄準美企高階主管報復。<br />\n<br />\n庫克說：「我不知道那件事的前因後果，我不需要知道也不該知道。但我可以告訴你，當我過去時，覺得受到歡迎。」<br />\n<br />\n近幾個月，庫克已經公開反對貿易緊張，甚至與美國總統川普討論此事。蘋果的供應鏈在中國紮根很深。該公司周三大幅下修財測，指中國經濟放緩是財測低於預期的主要原因。<br />\n<br />\n庫克說：「我確實認為，建立強有力的貿易關係符合兩國最佳利益。這是兩國之間的重大協議，極為複雜，顯然需要更新，這些都毫無疑問。企業可以發揮讓兩國團結合作的關鍵作用。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3571474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3571474&d=LzYF7DbOJ2VHvfr96iZeNNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3affc8a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3571474</a>"},{"pid":"f27c9a834f657f1b754dd1afa838efbf58ffa260","tid":966534,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10da56e305d416d40f5df922687204869e9b2150","tid":966534,"uid":56467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"真係捉左佢既話 啲左膠會有咩反應？"},{"pid":"f2f705f547ca6b96709ad0c1441bab0b68d5bc37","tid":966534,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f27c9a834f657f1b754dd1afa838efbf58ffa260","tid":966534,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"奶共奶得正<br />\n怕咩抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54366d3931652d02ff3428b6f421b1dd6c166961","tid":966534,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"庫克是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f457f2a770d6b973389e1018a3e983a86042b3","tid":966534,"uid":116331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"點會夠膽捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a299870e38ae41e1a292d3c1359926545ce3940c","tid":966534,"uid":997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"48f457f2a770d6b973389e1018a3e983a86042b3","tid":966534,"uid":116331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"點會夠膽捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:18:17.000Z","msg":"捉左佢將佢打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\napple重生"},{"pid":"ed19ac29af3702beb699cd58952b7c181ad09e87","tid":966534,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:18:36.000Z","msg":"佢呢D真係唔怕比人捉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7168013522a4456c21bdef553eb299f5795f7d73","tid":966534,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:26:16.000Z","msg":"中國工廠靠佢搵食架"},{"pid":"8395900187a9b652fc91385108543db26e58ca4f","tid":966534,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7168013522a4456c21bdef553eb299f5795f7d73","tid":966534,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01: